onMouseOut="nd();">
(<I>Ann.</I> <SPAN CLASS="small">XI</SPAN>.23 f.)</A>. This privilege Galba extended to all citizens in the Gallic tribes and communities that had favoured Vindex and himself; and at the same time he reduced the tribute 25 per cent.
	<A HREF="
